attributionInfo.mlsDisclaimer: Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Fox & Roach, REALTORS® is part of HomeServices of America, the nation’s largest provider of total home services and largest residential brokerage company in the U.S. in sales, according to the 2022 REAL Trends 500 report. The company was named “Real Estate Agency Brand of the Year” and was recently awarded Top Workplaces in 2022.  With over 5000 sales professionals in more than 75 sales offices across the Tri-State area, the company was recently acknowledged as #1, for the seventh year in a row, in the entire national Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Network. Through its affiliated services, the Trident Group and Prosperity Home Mortgage, LLC; the company provides one-stop shopping and facilitated services to its clients including mortgage financing, and title, property and casualty insurance. The company-sponsored charitable foundation, Fox & Roach/Trident Charities, is committed to addressing the needs of children and families in stressful life circumstances and has contributed over $8 million to more than 250 local organizations since its inception in 1995. Visit us at www.foxroach.com

data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming end-of-row property boasts a prime location with easy access to parks and schools. Inside, you'll find three ample-sized bedrooms, ideal for accommodating your family or guests. The finished basement, complete with a half bath, is perfect for entertaining and is the only home on the block that leads to a private backyard, offering a serene outdoor space for relaxation and gatherings. Additionally, a private sunroom off the dining area provides a cozy spot for morning coffee or quiet evenings.This well-maintained home is move-in ready, just waiting for you to make it your own. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to embrace a comfortable and convenient lifestyle in this delightful end-of-row home. Schedule a viewing today to explore all the possibilities it has to offer! 2023-12-14
